Apparently, NOBODY bothered to test 2.4.18-pre*, 2.4.18 final,
or 2.4.19-pre* on s390. The broken patch went into 2.4.18-pre1
with a curt changelog:
- S390 merge                                    (IBM)
Patch attached.
-- Pete
